<lyrics>[V1]
 1- tsạmy̱ ạlḥb bynnạ ḥty̱ kmạ knt nkwn
 fy wḥdẗ jmʿtnạ sẖkraⁿạ lk rby ạlḥnwn
 ạlqrạr - yswʿ ạ̉nt rbnạ fy ʿmrnạ fy qlbnạ
 yswʿ ạ̉nt qwtnạ klạmk srạjnạ
 2- ạ̉wṣytny ạ̉ṣwnhạ ạ̉ḍmhạ fy ạ̉ḍlʿy
 ạ̉ḥbhạ ạ̉ḥyṭhạ ạ̉mnaⁿạ wfyk nḥtmy
 3- ạ̉wṣytny ạ̉ṣwnh ạ̉ʿṭyh ywmy wgẖdy
 rạ̉sy ykwn bynmạ ạ̉nt ạ̉sạs ạlmnzl
 4- nltṣq bbʿḍnạ fyk nṣyr wạḥdạaⁿ
 fy bytnạ nṭyʿk ạ̉nt tkwn ḥạrsạaⁿ</lyrics>
<title>tsạmy̱ ạlḥb</title>
</song>